This paper deals with optimization frameworks for semi-supervised and transfer learning, which are topics that are commonly studied in the machine learning community. The use of multiple classifiers and clusterers is also a common technique in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
